{"type":"message","id":"a54ece35","parentId":"3dfbcac0","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:39:03.232Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<active-task-guard>\nSource: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\nStatus: active\nUse this only as the recovery rail for the current multi-step task.\nIf the user's latest message is a continuation, continue from Current, update ACTIVE_TASK.md after each minimum deliverable, and immediately promote the next item.\nIf the user's latest message is clearly unrelated, do not force this task.\n\nGoal:\n- 从零实现 day1-3 风格的 A 股日频均值回归信号模块，并接入现有 personal-a-share-research-system 的信号/回测链路\n\nAcceptance:\n- 产出新的策略说明或配置文件，明确 day1-3 信号规则、市场状态门控与接入方式\n- 产出至少一个可运行脚本，能生成标准化 `date,instrument,score` 信号文件或直接进入现有回测链路\n- 产出一次最小验收结果（脚本运行输出、报告或日志），证明首版实现已能被系统读取/验证\n\nCurrent:\n- 增加相对HS300超额收益过滤（excess_ret5 特征），修改 day1_3_config.yaml + 信号脚本\n\nNext:\n- [ ] 评估下一轮需要补强的规则（信号打分精度、候选股质量、市场宽度计算等）\n\nRecent Evidence:\n- **配置文件**: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/day1_3_config.yaml`\n- **Smoke test 产物**:\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/day1_3_candidates_20260310.csv`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv`\n\nIntegrity Warnings:\n- None\n\nBlockers:\n- None\n</active-task-guard>\n\n[Sat 2026-03-21 17:39 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 为 day1-3 均值回归信号模块增加 excess_ret5（相对 HS300 超额收益）特征与过滤逻辑。\n\n## 背景\n- 项目路径：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system`\n- 已有配置：`config/day1_3_config.yaml`（含信号打分、候选股过滤、市场状态门控）\n- 已有信号脚本：需找到生成 `day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_*.csv` 的 Python 脚本（搜索 `signals/` 或 `scripts/` 目录）\n- 已有 smoke test 数据：`data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv`\n\n## 任务清单\n\n### 1. 读取现有文件\n- 读取 `config/day1_3_config.yaml`\n- 找到信号生成主脚本（搜索 signals/ scripts/ 目录中生成 day1_3_mean_reversion_factor 的 py 文件）\n- 读取 smoke test 输出 `data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv` 前几行了解字段\n\n### 2. 修改 day1_3_config.yaml\n在 `features` 或过滤规则中增加 excess_ret5（个股 5 日收益率 - HS300 同期收益率）相关配置：\n- 新增特征：`excess_ret5`（计算方式：个股 ret5 - HS300 ret5）\n- 可选：在打分体系中加入 excess_ret5 权重，或作为硬过滤条件（e.g. excess_ret5 < 0 才入选，排除跑输大盘的）\n- 推荐作为硬过滤：excess_ret5 < 0（只选超跌且相对大盘也跌得多的），或设置阈值如 excess_ret5 < -1%\n\n### 3. 修改信号生成脚本\n- 接入 HS300 数据（使用 akshare 或 tushare 获取 HS300 成分或指数数据）\n- 计算每只股票的 excess_ret5 = ret5 - hs300_ret5\n- 将 excess_ret5 应用到过滤逻辑（硬过滤或打分加权）\n- 保持输出字段兼容 `date,instrument,score` 标准格式\n\n### 4. 重新运行 smoke test\n- 日期使用 20260310（或脚本支持的最早数据日）\n- 验证 excess_ret5 过滤生效\n- 检查产物文件格式正确\n\n### 5. 更新配置与证据\n- 更新 `config/day1_3_config.yaml` 记录 excess_ret5 特征说明\n- 记录新生成的信号文件路径\n\n## 交付物\n1. 更新的 `config/day1_3_config.yaml`\n2. 修改后的信号生成脚本\n3. 新版 smoke test 产物（CSV/JSON）\n4. 运行日志或摘要\n\n## 约束\n- 不改变已有的 `date,instrument,score` 标准输出格式\n- 不删除现有功能，只增量增加 excess_ret5\n- HS300 数据优先用 akshare，其次 tushare，再次用 Yahoo Finance"}],"timestamp":1774085943230}}
{"type":"message","id":"55b0f2ca","parentId":"a54ece35","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:39:07.593Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me start by reading the existing files to understand the current structure.","thinkingSignature":"b8c424344bd0f4b8d23b18362930f8b2c53e55250507dbe7427d1f19d97fce75"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i174peu7xmmn_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/day1_3_config.yaml"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i174peu7xmmn_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv","limit":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58,"output":133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":22344,"totalTokens":22535,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774085943231}}
{"type":"message","id":"434b8f49","parentId":"55b0f2ca","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:39:07.613Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i174peu7xmmn_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# ============================================================\n# day1_3_config.yaml\n# A股日频均值回归信号模块 · 标准化配置文件\n# 版本: v1.0.0\n# 描述: T日收盘特征计算 → T+1 开盘买入均值回归/超跌反弹策略\n# 接入方式: overlay (作为 rd_agent_integration.yaml 的因子叠加层)\n# ============================================================\n\nenabled: true\n\n# -------------------- 信号基本信息 --------------------\nsignal:\n  name: day1_3_mean_reversion\n  version: \"1.0.0\"\n  description: |\n    日频均值回归/超跌反弹信号（day1-3 风格）。\n    基于最近5日收益率（ret5）、当前价距MA10偏离度（dist_ma10）、\n    20日价格区间位置（range_pos20）三个维度对全市场股票打分，\n    结合市场状态门控（strong/neutral/weak）调节总仓位，\n    T日收盘决策、T+1开盘成交。\n  author: quant-research-system\n  date_range:\n    start: \"2019-01-01\"\n    end: \"2026-12-31\"\n\n# -------------------- 股票池过滤规则 --------------------\nstock_pool:\n  # 基础价格与市值过滤\n  min_price: 3.0                    # 最低股价（元）\n  min_total_mv: 1000000             # 最低总市值（万元）\n  max_total_mv: 30000000            # 最高总市值（万元）\n  min_turnover_rate: 0.0            # 最低换手率（%）\n  max_turnover_rate: 25.0           # 最高换手率（%）\n\n  # 涨跌停过滤\n  exclude_limit_up: true             # 排除涨停股（避免次日高开低走）\n  exclude_limit_down: true          # 排除跌停股\n  limit_up_threshold: 0.099         # 涨停阈值（涨幅>=9.9%视为涨停）\n  limit_down_threshold: -0.099      # 跌停阈值\n\n  # 特殊股票过滤\n  exclude_st: true                   # 排除ST/*ST股票\n  exclude_new_stock_days: 60        # 排除上市不足N日的次新股\n\n  # 北向资金/杠杆资金过滤\n  north_flow_required: false        # 是否要求北向资金持股（暂未启用）\n\n  # 成交额最低门槛\n  min_amount: 100000                # 最低日成交额（元），过滤僵尸股\n\n# -------------------- 历史数据配置 --------------------\nhistory:\n  csv: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/data/a_stock_history.csv\n  lookback_calendar_days: 220       # 最少需要的历史数据天数\n  min_history_bars: 40              # 最少需要的K线条数\n  date_col: trade_date\n  symbol_col: ts_code\n  close_col: close\n  open_col: open\n  high_col: high\n  low_col: low\n  amount_col: amount\n  encoding: utf-8\n\n# -------------------- 指数/大盘数据 --------------------\nmarket:\n  index_csv: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/index_sh000300.csv\n  index_code: \"000300.SH\"           # 沪深300作为大盘基准\n  date_col: date\n  close_col: close\n  ma_window: 20                     # 均线窗口\n  breadth_ma_window: 20             # 市场宽度均线窗口\n\n  # -------------------- 市场状态门控阈值 --------------------\n  # 状态判断逻辑：\n  #   strong : 沪深300收盘价/MA20 >= 1.02  且 近期交易日>60天\n  #   neutral: 沪深300收盘价/MA20 >= -0.03（默认状态）\n  #   weak   : 沪深300收盘价/MA20 < -0.03\n  regime_thresholds:\n    strong_index_trend_min: 0.02    # strong 最低指数趋势阈值\n    weak_index_trend_floor: -0.03   # weak 指数趋势下限\n\n  # 仓位调节系数（按市场状态）\n  scale_by_regime:\n    strong:  1.0\n    neutral: 0.6\n    weak:    0.3\n\n  # 市场宽度辅助阈值（预留，暂用指数趋势）\n  breadth_thresholds:\n    strong_breadth: 0.58\n    neutral_breadth: 0.48\n\n# -------------------- 信号特征计算规则 --------------------\nfeatures:\n  # ret5: 最近5日收益率（复利）\n  #   计算: close_T / close_{T-5} - 1\n  #   过滤: <= max_ret5 (避免强势股追高)\n  ret5:\n    window: 5\n    max_value: 0.05                  # 过滤涨幅>5%的股票\n\n  # dist_ma10: 当前价距10日均线偏离度\n  #   计算: close / ma10 - 1\n  #   过滤: <= max_dist_ma10 (避免已大涨股票)\n  dist_ma10:\n    window: 10\n    min_periods: 5\n    max_value: 0.10                 # 偏离度不超过10%\n    # 权重越高 → 越偏好超跌/低位股\n\n  # range_pos20: 20日价格区间位置\n  #   计算: (close - ll20) / (hh20 - ll20)\n  #   过滤: <= max_range_pos20 (避免已在高位)\n  range_pos20:\n    window: 20\n    min_periods: 10\n    max_value: 0.80                 # 位于区间80%以下\n\n  # reversal_bar: 当日反转棒（可选）\n  reversal_bar:\n    enabled: false\n    direction: negative              # 期望当日下跌（正值越大越优先）\n    weight: 0.10\n\n  # 综合打分权重\n  scoring_weights:\n    dist_ma10:   0.30               # 均线偏离权重\n    ret5:        0.25               # 5日收益率权重\n    excess_ret5: 0.20                # 超额收益权重（预留）\n    range_pos20: 0.15               # 区间位置权重\n    reversal:    0.10               # 反转棒权重\n\n# -------------------- 仓位计算规则 --------------------\nposition:\n  # 总仓位上限（按市场状态调节后）\n  total_exposure: 0.72              # 目标总仓位（72%）\n\n  # 单股仓位上限\n  max_single_weight: 0.08           # 单只股票最高权重（8%）\n\n  # 等权+分数加权混合\n  #   raw_weights = score（百分位分数）\n  #   norm_weights = raw_weights / sum(raw_weights) * total_exposure\n  #   norm_weights = clip(norm_weights, max=max_single_weight)\n  weighting_method: score_percentile  # score_percentile | equal_weight | risk_parity\n\n  # 最小候选股数（不足时降低总仓位）\n  min_candidates: 5\n  min_total_weight_if_short: 0.20   # 候选不足时最低总仓位\n\n  # 最大候选股数\n  top_k: 12                         # 最多选入 N 只\n\n# -------------------- 信号输出字段约定 --------------------\n# 标准信号文件字段（与 rd_agent_integration.yaml 完全对齐）\n# 用途: 供 backtest 模块读取\nsignal_output:\n  # RD因子文件（因子分数，直接供 rd_agent 叠加使用）\n  rd_factor:\n    path_template: \"{rd_factor_dir}/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_{date}.csv\"\n    fields:\n      - name: date\n        type: str\n        format: \"YYYY-MM-DD\"\n        description: 决策日期（T日）\n      - name: instrument\n        type: str\n        format: \"XXXXXX.XX\"\n        description: 股票代码（带后缀 .SH/.SZ/.BJ）\n      - name: score\n        type: float\n        description: 综合打分（0~1，越高越优先）\n    encoding: utf-8\n\n  # 候选股详情文件（人读报告）\n  candidates:\n    path_template: \"{candidate_dir}/day1_3_candidates_{date}.csv\"\n    fields:\n      - name: trade_date\n        type: str\n        format: \"YYYY-MM-DD\"\n        description: 交易日期\n      - name: ts_code\n        type: str\n        description: 股票代码\n      - name: close\n        type: float\n        description: 当日收盘价\n      - name: ret5\n        type: float\n        description: 5日收益率\n      - name: dist_ma10\n        type: float\n        description: 均线偏离度\n      - name: range_pos20\n        type: float\n        description: 20日区间位置\n      - name: score\n        type: float\n        description: 综合分数\n      - name: target_weight\n        type: float\n        description: 目标持仓权重\n    encoding: utf-8\n\n  # 原始信号文件（供风控/实盘队列使用）\n  raw_signal:\n    path_template: \"{raw_signal_dir}/day1_3_mean_reversion_{date}.csv\"\n    fields:\n      - name: trade_date\n        type: str\n        description: 决策日期\n      - name: ts_code\n        type: str\n        description: 股票代码\n      - name: signal_type\n        type: str\n        enum: [BUY, SELL, HOLD]\n        description: 信号方向\n      - name: score\n        type: float\n        description: 综合打分\n      - name: target_weight\n        type: float\n        description: 目标权重\n      - name: strategy_id\n        type: str\n        description: 策略标识（固定 day1_3_mean_reversion）\n      - name: risk_flag\n        type: str\n        enum: [strong, neutral, weak]\n        description: 市场状态标签\n      - name: comment\n        type: str\n        description: 备注（含 regime、trend 等关键信息）\n      - name: source_run_id\n        type: str\n        description: 运行ID（格式: day1_3_{date_compact}）\n      - name: generated_at\n        type: str\n        description: 生成时间（ISO8601，带Asia/Shanghai时区）\n    encoding: utf-8\n\n# -------------------- 与 rd_agent_integration.yaml 的接入方式 --------------------\nintegration:\n  # 接入模式: overlay | standalone | replace\n  #   overlay   : 因子分数叠加到现有base信号之上（推荐）\n  #   standalone: 独立运行，不影响其他策略\n  #   replace   : 完全替换现有base信号\n  mode: overlay\n\n  # rd_agent_integration.yaml 中的 key 引用\n  rd_config_key: rd_agent_integration_day1_3\n\n  # 叠加权重（overlay模式生效）\n  blend_with_rd:\n    day1_3_weight: 0.25            # 均值回归信号权重\n    base_weight: 0.75               # 基础RD因子权重\n    fill_missing_score: 0.0         # 缺失时填充值\n\n  # backtest 参数（与 rd_agent_integration.yaml 保持一致）\n  backtest:\n    topk: 10\n    n_drop: 1\n    hold_thresh: 4\n    risk_degree: 0.5\n    breadth_profile:\n      low_th: 0.48\n      mid_th: 0.55\n      low_scale: 0.30\n      mid_scale: 0.60\n      high_scale: 0.95\n\n# -------------------- 输出目录 --------------------\noutputs:\n  candidate_dir: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports\n  rd_factor_dir: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/rd_agent\n  raw_signal_dir: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/signals/raw\n  summary_dir: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports\n\n# -------------------- 财务/基本面数据 --------------------\nfundamentals:\n  csv: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/daily_basic_all_2019_2026.csv\n  # 已在 stock_pool.min_price / min_total_mv 等字段覆盖\n\n# -------------------- 执行参数 --------------------\nexecution:\n  # 是否T+1开盘成交（固定规则，不建议修改）\n  execution_mode: T_plus_1_open     # T+1_open | T_closes\n\n  # 是否输出盘中预览（用于人工确认）\n  intraday_preview: false\n\n  # 随机种子（确保回测可复现）\n  random_seed: 42\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774085947606}}
